#. module: account_period_and_fiscalyear
#: model:ir.actions.act_window,help:account_period_and_fiscalyear.action_account_fiscalyear
msgid ""
"Define your company's financial year according to your needs. A\n"
"                financial year is a period at the end of which a company's\n"
"                accounts are made up (usually 12 months). The financial year is\n"
"                usually referred to by the date in which it ends. For example,\n"
"                if a company's financial year ends November 30, 2011, then\n"
"                everything between December 1, 2010 and November 30, 2011\n"
"                would be referred to as FY 2011."
msgstr ""
"Defina el Periodo Fiscal de su Compañía de acuerdo a sus necesidades.\n"
"Un Periodo Fiscal corresponde al periodo donde se registra la información\n"
"contable (generalmente 12 meses).s\n"
"El Periodo Fiscal tiene una fecha inicial y final, por ejemplo del 1º de Enero\n"
"al 31 de Diciembre de 2011, este Periodo Fiscal podría llamarse: PF2011."

